<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL2">
<l>paccaimā malaipōl mēṉi pavaḷavāy kamalac ceṅkaṇ</l>
<l>accutā vamara rēṟē yāyartaṅ koḻuntē yeṉṉu</l>
<l>miccuvai tavira yāṉpō yintira lōka māḷu</l>
<l>maccuvai peṟiṉum vēṇṭē ṉaraṅkamā nakaru ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Other than this taste [obtained from] saying --</l>
<l>‘O Acyuta with a body like a big, green mountain, coral lips, [and] red lotus eyes!</l>
<l>O Bull among the immortals! O Scion of the cowherds!’ --</l>
<l>Even if I were to get that taste [derived from] going and ruling over Indra’s world,</l>
<l>I would not want [it], O You who are in the big city of Raṅgam!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
